text.tspan: Handles requests it is responsible for.
Defines an interface for handling requests.
Initiates the request to a ConcreteHandler object on the chain.
Avoid coupling the sender of a request to its receiver by giving more than one object a
chance to handle the request. Chain the receiving objects and pass the request along the
chain until an object handles it.
If the ConcreteHandler can handle the request, it does so; otherwise it forwards the request
